items.title: Timmy Trumpet X Sam Feldt - Sun Comes Up (ft. EKKO x Joe Taylor)
items.description:
Stream/download: https://orcd.co/suncomesup

Prepare to ignite the dance floor as global music sensations Timmy Trumpet and Sam Feldt join forces to unleash their latest single, 'Sun Comes Up’, out this May only via Smash The House!

This dynamic collaboration sees the two maestros of electronic music crafting a pulsating house track that marries Timmy Trumpet's signature brass-infused energy with Sam Feldt's soulful deep house vibes. 'Sun Comes Up' is a journey that leans into electro tendencies while seamlessly weaving in glitching synth lines and deep house tropes. With guitar lines strumming to set the tone of the melody, the production value ramps up the ante, delivering an irresistible creation that will have audiences two-stepping along to its infectious beat. 

Timmy Trumpet and Sam Feldt, both renowned for their innovative approaches to music production, effortlessly blend their individual styles to create a track that is as electrifying as it is immersive. 'Sun Comes Up' captures the essence of a euphoric sunrise, evoking a sense of warmth and joy that is bound to resonate with listeners worldwide. With its irresistible rhythm and undeniable groove, 'Sun Comes Up' is poised to become a summer anthem, solidifying Timmy Trumpet and Sam Feldt's status as top-tier names in the scene.

Teaming up on the track's vocals are singer-songwriters Ekko and Joe Taylor, two celebrated musicians in their own right. London-based artist Ekko’s vocals add a majestic layer to the track with the renowned emotional depth signature to her work. Ekko’s tracks have amassed over 50 million streams on Spotify alone and draw in over 1 million monthly listeners. 

A master of his craft; Joe Taylor is responsible for some of the most exciting tracks in dance music. Coming from a background in songwriting for international superstars, Joe now boasts a collection huge collaboration tracks with millions of streams. From the lyrical flow to the impressionable vocal delivery, the pairing of Ekko and Joe Taylor adds an uplifting texture to Timmy Trumpet and Sam Feldt’s already feel-good soundscape.

items.title: Dimitri Vegas & Like Mike x Maddix x Da Hool ft. Kiki Solvej - Meet Her At The Love Parade
items.description:
Stream/download: https://orcd.co/meetherattheloveparade

Smash The House honchos Dimitri Vegas & Like Mike join forces with the prominent Dutch DJ and Producer Maddix to put a new age spin on an unmistakable classic rave anthem. Featuring the vocal sounds of the exemplary Kiki Solvej, the trio of acts have injected Da Hool’s 1997 ‘Meet Her At The Love Parade’ with an infectious techno-trance style that gives the timeless track an exciting new revamp.

The new track is a raver’s delight that combines elements of techno with its heavy fist-pumping kick beat and the high-paced cluster of hats and claps with trance-like synths and acid-heavy basslines. Sirens pierce through the beat creating moments of intensity and amplifying the build-ups. Kiki’s echoing voice can be heard throughout as it harmonizes with the track vocalizing lyrics in her native German tongue to add a layer of shade and mystery to the composition. 

Paying homage to one of dance music's most celebrated works, the original sample from Da Hool’s ‘Meet Her At The Love Parade’ is featured periodically throughout the track. The catchy synth loop is a familiar pattern that brings nostalgia to listeners around the globe. Now, this dancefloor classic has a new burst of energy, courtesy of some of modern dance music’s biggest players.
